title: Top Places to visit in Chhindwara, Madhya Pradesh
content: Chhindwara is city in India and a Municipal Corporation in Chhindwara district in the Indian state of Madhya Pradesh. It is known as the "Corn City" of India. is the administrative headquarters of Chhindwara District. Chhindwara is reachable by rail or road from adjacent cities Nagpur and Jabalpu
